There are hidden tunnnels under the whole city with secret entries, you can actually walk to every part of Freeport including the port through underground. Since at the port there is just one guard patrolling infrequently you can reach the dock without getting whacked. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Even some evil guilds like rogues and I believe Shadowknights can be found in the underground tunnels and caves as well, where evil races can sell and train if needed. Just what I found out while traveling through Norrath...if you evil people are interested I could show those entries to you <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Farewell !!<br>
Teny</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/udespaire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Despaire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#006400>(8/17/00 2:45:38 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Dark Race travel guide</span><hr size=1> ...excepting for Trolls and Ogres who are KOS even in the sewers of Freeport....<br>
<br>
Despaire D'vie <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Kizor</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#006400>(8/18/00 3:44:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Dark Race Travel Guide</span><hr size=1> Got a Question.  I'm in Lesser Faydark fighting the sisters and i wanna kill some orcs but that lowers my faction with my fellow Tier'Dal.  Is there anything that raizes (i can't spell) faction with the DE's so i could hunt the crushbone orcs also? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/udespaire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Despaire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#006400>(8/18/00 4:23:04 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Dark Race Travel Guide</span><hr size=1> I believe killing high elf slaves does... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/urazgum.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Razgum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#006400>(8/21/00 4:07:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Dark Race Travel Guide</span><hr size=1> Okay.....I think I'm going to rethink my Travel Guide idea.  My attempt to travel from Butcherblock to Kunark than to Oasis end up with the loss of my body (I belive a glitch) and a full bubble of xp.<br>
<br>
Note to self:  Listen to Dispaire! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Hopefully I can petition a GM to reclaim my lost body.<br>
<br>
I would also like to thank Ollen (sp) for helping me out and putting up with my frustration.  Thanks to everyone else who offered up support during that little night o' fun....hehehehehehe<br>
