<br>
Okay..... I will forget travelling through Kunark until I'm at least level 60!!!!  While swimming around near the port in Butcherblock the big boat came in and I decided to see if I could board it as suggested on EQAtlas.  It worked! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    Once in Freeport and jumped off the boat before it docked and swam to the secret entrace to the Freeport Sewers.  From there I made my way to East Freeport and travel became relatively safe again. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
